%% Sequence Diagram Template -- API Call
%% Replace actor/participant names with actual components.
%% Add/remove steps as needed.

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant Auth as Auth Provider
    participant API as REST Controller
    participant Svc as Service Layer
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Initiate action
    UI->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>UI: Token valid

    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/resource
    API->>API: Validate request body
    API->>Svc: processResource(dto)
    Svc->>DB: INSERT resource
    DB-->>Svc: Saved entity
    Svc-->>API: ResourceResponse
    API-->>UI: 201 Created
    UI-->>User: Success confirmation
